{"tid":2057793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年71一定要搞個反警暴HongKonger Lives Matter遊行","createTime":"2020-06-09T15:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T11:41:21.000Z","uid":291309,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6b55b1e0a623ef88bfa2eac95eb9c3477fa273","tid":2057793,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"食住外國BlackLivesMatter既水<br />\n我地可以反警暴，叫埋南亞手足出黎<br />\n外國傳媒一定會報<br />\n<br />\n如果黑警愈暴力清場，就愈要比國際睇下<br />\n同全世界講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Police Brutality happens in Hong Kong everyday and even worse!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n外國左膠見到可能會支持<br />\n宜家佢地個個focus住美國示威<br />\n若我地宜家講Police Brutality好容易會得到國際關注<br />\n<br />\n要連結國際<br />\n我地要再次將個焦點帶返黎香港/中國呢邊<br />\n帶出香港警暴問題比美國更嚴重呢個訊息<br />\n<br />\n要比現在支持BlackLivesMatter既人知道中共都係佢地敵人！<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議71遊行其中一個重點主題要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反警暴</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HongKonger Lives Matter</span></strong> too!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928df0846b931ef9b95b4df31f3344be714e04ac","tid":2057793,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2b88707aa72a769c1d5fa87ea46d7a9d58191e","tid":2057793,"uid":307203,"like":